Boxing drill• “landing the 1-2”

Try this to land that jab cross aka “1-2” more effectively! 

Feint the first jab to drawl out a reaction, close the distance with the second jab and put the cross behind it! If you get them going backwards your in business to land this!

I love hittin the heavy bag bare knuckle. Let’s you dig and drive ya knucks in w precision to practice a perfect punch and really pop the bag. The heavy bag is one of the best tools for a fighter. Ppl wanna do fancy shit and hit pads all the time but w the bag we can really go to work and develop power, speed, and technique. Takes focus & discipline sometimes at 1st but u fall in love. Bare knuck toughens up ya hands 2👊👊

📸 @alexweinraub
